column10: I like the questions it asks, it helps to be able to give as many clues as possible to be able to find the answer.
column11: I found it hard to find the signs for backpack, and another one I did not know. They were two handed signs that moved, and most of the answers I got only used one hand, even though I selected two hands moving. So if it would just show two handed movements. Other than that this program is set up really well and I think it would be very useful and helpful.

column10: I liked the questions it asked, also helpful to be able to tell the search what youre looking for.
column11: A little hard to understand the questions, and sometimes did not even give me any answers which was a little frustrating. Other than that it was helpful.
